similareditors-error-database-refresh: Error message displayed when there is a database refresh in progress, temporarily blocking access
similareditors-error-default: Error message displayed when no error key is specified
similareditors-error-user-bot: Error message displayed when the target is a bot
similareditors-error-user-no-account: Error message displayed when the target has no account
similareditors-error-user-no-edits: Error message displayed when the target has no relevant edits, or perhaps no account
similareditors-form-field-target-label: Label for a form field on [[Special:SimilarEditors]]
similareditors-form-field-target-placeho: Placeholder for a text input on [[Special:SimilarEditors]]
similareditors-form-submit: Label for the submit button on [[Special:SimilarEditors]]
similareditors-no-results: Notice that might display on [[Special:SimilarEditors]] after form submission
similareditors-overlap-level-low: Qualitative description of a similarity score between two editors. See also {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-high}}, {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-medium}}, {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-none}}.
similareditors-overlap-level-medium:
Qualitative description of a similarity score between two editors. See also {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-high}}, {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-low}}, {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-none}}.
{{identical|Medium}}
similareditors-overlap-level-no-overlap: Qualitative description of a similarity score between two editors. See also {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-high}}, {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-low}}, {{msg-mw|similareditors-overlap-level-medium}}.
similareditors-results-user-timeline: Link text for additional information related to the user
similareditors-summary: Description of what SimilarEditors does, displayed on [[Special:SimilarEditors]]
similareditors-survey-freeform-text-labe: Placeholder for a text input in the feedback survey on [[Special:SimilarEditors]]. The placeholder should be blank, but the message must be defined (and not be an empty string) in order for the input to display.
similareditors-survey-question: Question asked in the feedback survey on [[Special:SimilarEditors]]
